    <item>
      <title>特朗普对加密货币的热情</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/crypto-s-trump-enthusiasm-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Delta Blockchain Fund 普通合伙人 Kavita Gupta 表示，唐纳德·特朗普的当选是加密货币的最大福音，因为市场期待新政府对加密货币有更多澄清。她与 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 一起在“彭博科技”上进行讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/crypto-s-trump-enthusiasm-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 20:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果合法，DraftKings 将在体育之外扩张业务：首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/draftkings-would-expand-outside-of-sports-if-legal-ceo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普重返总统宝座之际，彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 讨论了 CHIPS 法案的未来，DraftKings 首席执行官 Jason Robins 也加入了讨论，介绍了他们的最新收益和修订后的预测。此外，在特朗普 2.0 的领导下，加密货币可能会获得巨大推动。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-08/draftkings-would-expand-outside-of-sports-if-legal-ceo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 20:06:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>流动性紧缩导致玻利维亚放宽黄金持有限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/bolivia-eases-rules-on-gold-holdings-as-liquidity-crunch-bites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玻利维亚央行正在放宽国家黄金储备的规定，这可能使其获得更多流动性来支付进口费用并解决严重的燃料短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/bolivia-eases-rules-on-gold-holdings-as-liquidity-crunch-bites</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 20:05:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨，延续自六月以来的最佳周涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/dollar-jumps-to-extend-its-best-weekly-winning-streak-since-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周五上涨，延续受唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫推动的周度涨势，并导致主要货币下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/dollar-jumps-to-extend-its-best-weekly-winning-streak-since-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 18:26:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
